Revision history for Data-SimplePath

0.001	2009/08/16
	* Initial release

0.002	2013/03/06
	* First CPAN release
	* Modified some tests in t/14-get.t to not use qr//
	* Synopsis modified to avoid test warnings
	* Moved Test::* to BUILD_REQUIRES in Makefile.PL

0.003	2013/03/08
	* Changed -tT command line option to -T in some tests to avoid test
	  failures with (very) old Perl versions

0.004	2013/03/13
	* Missed one -tT command line option in 0.003

0.005	2013/04/10
	* Updated documentation
